snippet.title: The 3D Print General
snippet.description:
Everything 3D Printed! I showcase FDM tutorials, tips, and lots of fun builds.  Highly detailed 2020 3D printing failures book out now! https://amzn.to/2pQGOfc

You can also visit http://3dprintgeneral.com/ for further tips, as well as a store of products I use and trust!

Support the channel with unique 3D printing shirts and sweatshirts: https://teespring.com/stores/3d-print-general-merch

Grab all of our exclusive 3D designs for only a $1 donation! https://www.patreon.com/3DPrintGeneral
